Moula Applications Privacy Policy
To improve product support and development, you agree that Moula or other third party companies may use different technologies to collect, use, store and transmit technical information regarding your mobile device (including unique device id), geo-location, IP address, device brand and model, OS, software and applications and application usage data for analysis purposes, which can't be personally identifiable. Moula and/or third parties may also collect, store, use and/or transmit game play or session data, browsers IDs, carrier companies informations and online and applications usage metrics, statistics and/or analytic data, which are also anonymous.
Third parties usage, collection, storage and transfering of data are subject to the third partyâ€™s privacy policy. Some of the third parties that use that information in most Moula applications are Google Analytics and Facebook. Moula applications and games use Google Analytics to help analyze how users use the app, and Facebook to provide rankings and login in certain games. Information about applications usage for analytic purposes and IP address are sent to Google servers. This information is used for visitors statistical analysis of Moula's applications and games usage.
We will never use the statistical analytics tools to track or to collect any Personally Identifiable Information (PII) of visitors to our applications and games, except when you explicitly agree to that by signin up using Facebook. Google will not associate your IP address with any other data held by Google. We will not associate any data gathered from this application with any other Personally Identifiable Information from any other source. All ads displayed in Moula's apps and games are provided by Google Admob.
Using Moula's applications and games, means you agree to the terms of this privacy policy. If you do not want to accept the terms present in this privacy policy, please don't use our applications and games. Continued use of our apps and games after any changes or additions to this privacy policy will also mean your acceptance of the changes and/or new terms. 
		For questions about this privacy policy please contact us at: info@moulasoftware.com